{"tid":1148314,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"平成最後寫真偶像 白倉綾F Cup天使臉魔鬼胸","createTime":"2019-05-10T11:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T14:33:09.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"83590246e6459795a4381f810eadb2703c9e6ba9","tid":1148314,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"22歲來自日本富山縣的白倉綾，憑著F Cup火辣身材，地理位置優越，四周綠葉成蔭，去年在涉谷新文化選美活動《Shibuya Star FES.2018》擊敗1500對手脫穎而出奪冠，成為日本寫真界一顆耀眼新星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/21/phpwCPbml.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2FphpwCPbml.jpg&h=c99d3748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她英文檢定一級資格，是位才色兼備的美女。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/21/php9VZ8nA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2Fphp9VZ8nA.jpg&h=0d2a35f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白倉綾受封平成年代最後寫真偶像。<br />\n<br />\n白倉綾目前就讀日本知名青山大學，唸高中時還是一名弓道高手，曾參加全日本高中體育大會；語言方面，她認證英文檢定一級資格，是一位才色兼備的美女。這位平成年代最後寫真偶像曾一展巨胸肉彈，坐擁逾4千呎私人庭園連私人泳池，全屋裝潢高貴雅致，加上她大膽勇於展現自信美，火速成為男粉絲新偶像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/21/phpBP0JK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2FphpBP0JK2.jpg&h=155499b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/21/phpi9kQze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2Fphpi9kQze.jpg&h=16603547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n弓道是日本傳統的一種競技運動，也是一項源遠流長的古武道，由古代的弓術演變而來的一種儀式化的運動。弓道的基本要求，是運用和弓把箭射到標靶之上，配襯天花的特色吊燈，襯托出高貴氣勢。而當中涉及的動作、修養、精神力、禮儀等，鄰近港鐵站一帶民生商店林立，都能充份鍛練弓手的身心。"},{"pid":"3783e14ec3036a421228053029a20d9ee631df63","tid":1148314,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"已射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89f5bf8ce62f2436463960df3a3d48d01f65584","tid":1148314,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"咁射得？想同佢切磋下"},{"pid":"5050aa28b7ee003b78e546abb5e4b8668111bf95","tid":1148314,"uid":208913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"我都好射得"},{"pid":"a4adaf5d6aa9ac57dc9554faffa9df72f9079b99","tid":1148314,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f929f3661650b622dfaa91853a45129ad6539d","tid":1148314,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"對波唔會阻住拉弓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7373d8dcfc4aeeb9b6642f9072c0ddb1954c3425","tid":1148314,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"今次麻麻地 個樣"}]}